Title: Impey EasyFit level dec and edp1 1200 x 750mm
Description: A high-strength 22mm thick GRP floorboard replacement, the Impey 1200 x 750mm Level-Dec EasyFit wet room floor former has an eccentric 360° rotating drain for ease of fitting and three locating rings ensuring a reliable hold between former and drain plate. Withstanding weights of up to 300kg, or 47 stone, with no need for under-boarding, the Level-Dec is made of tough SMC with a high glass content. Offering optional horizontal or vertical gravity drainage, four pre-formed drainage gradients and a round vinyl clamping drain, this floor former ensures level access in wetrooms finished with a vinyl floor covering.
